      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to be letting this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy it brings. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine shape; I\u2019ve looked after every inch of it. There might be a microscopic mark from a single Sunday drive, but you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find it! This isn't just a car; it's been my pride and joy. Come on over, let's chat cars, and see if she\u2019s the right fit for your garage!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
