      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in mechanical synergy. This chassis has been maintained to surgical standards, ensuring zero torsional flex and crisp turn-in response. The powerplant exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders with a power curve that remains linear through the entire rev range. We\u2019ve optimized the thermal management system and ensured the drivetrain operates with minimal parasitic drag. Every bushing is tight, and the gear synchronization is buttery. This isn't just a car; it's a precision-engineered instrument for the discerning pilot who understands the value of tight tolerances and preventative overhead. Truly a mint-spec specimen for the purist.",
